window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>CIA officer Jake Keller faces stakes that are very high and very personal in the latest electrifying thriller from the author of </b><b><i>Rogue Strike</i></b><b>. </b></p> <p>After years of relative calm, piracy has returned to the high sea. </p> <p>But the days of AK-47s and outboard engines are over. The new pirates hit like a SEAL team. Highly trained, and using cutting-edge technology, they make sure their victims are never heard from again. </p> <p>Ships and crews are vanishing at a staggering rate. </p> <p>As the threat to international shipping grows, US authorities become determined to find the source of this new danger. </p> <p>Jake Keller has a plan - to lure the pirate mastermind out of hiding by infiltrating his organization - but itâ€™s a dangerous gambit, made more so by Jake's personal involvement with the beautiful heiress to a Greek shipping fortune and an ulterior agenda coming out of CIA headquarters. </p> <p>As the threats close in from all sides, Jake finds himself faced with a familiar choice: back off, or go on the offensive. </p> <p>His fate, and the fate of a nation, hang on his decision.</p>"; 
